Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.12,0:00:06.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, Kousei,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.03,0:00:09.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to study the\Nsheet music over and over,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.95,0:00:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and play it again\Nand again and again.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.00,0:00:15.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's how you're going to perfect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just what the score calls for,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.21,0:00:20.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,just as the composer intended,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.47,0:00:23.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,perfectly and precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.47,0:00:26.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're off again! How many\Ntimes do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.97,0:00:28.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to bed until\Nyou can play that passage!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.97,0:00:33.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Take a good look at it! It's\Nall there in the sheet music!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arima's No. 1 again? Well, his mother\Nis a direct disciple of Mr. Hashimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.11,0:00:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet there's sheet music\N plastered onto those glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.17,0:00:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plus they'll hide the bruises\Nfrom when she hits him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.49,0:00:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He practices seven or eight\Nhours a day, right? Everyday!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.45,0:00:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When does he get to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.62,0:00:52.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Most people couldn't\Nstand a life like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.46,0:00:54.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He really is just like a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.21,0:00:57.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}None of them know\Nwhat they're talking about.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:01:01.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm the only one who's on Mom's side.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.77,0:02:37.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.27,0:02:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But will you be okay? What about\Npractice? Have you rehearsed together?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.49,0:02:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No worries! We'll figure it\Nout! Because we rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.95,0:02:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate us jocks!\NI can make you time to rehearse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.91,0:02:57.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, shouldn't you guys be in\Nschool? And whose bike is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:02:59.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't sweat the small stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.80,0:03:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just barely, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.30,0:03:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.59,0:03:11.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.71,0:03:12.50,Clang,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*Twitch*
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:13.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.39,0:03:14.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We made it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.47,0:03:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.42,0:03:15.75,Grab,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*Grab*
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.88,0:03:20.90,Menacing,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,*Drag*
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:18.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you both! We'll be going, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.73,0:03:21.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei, your shoes!\NSneakers aren't gonna cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:22.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Put mine on!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.27,0:03:23.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Hurry! Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.27,0:03:23.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Better than sneakers, at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.65,0:03:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tsubaki... Watari...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.65,0:03:27.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks. I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.24,0:03:32.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! We're cutting it close. Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:33.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Slow down a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:35.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.24,0:03:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You think Kousei\Ncan pull this off?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.67,0:03:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Spring will be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.96,0:03:50.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? It's almost May, when\Nthe cherry blossoms scatter.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.18,0:03:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. But... I just know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.64,0:03:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...that spring will come.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.90,0:04:06.40,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Towa Music Competition Committee Sponsor\NSecond Annual Towa Music Competition\NViolin - Middle School Divison
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.49,0:04:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next, No. 12, Nashida.\NPlease get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:15.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Your goal\Nis to go out on top!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.58,0:04:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am! I'm gonna try to\Ngo out on top... I-I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.24,0:04:19.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\i1}Oh, man, that's putting the pressure on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.41,0:04:24.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is beyond crazy. I should have\Nspent a lot of time practicing this,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.13,0:04:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}memorizing it with\Nmy whole body,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}fine-tuning it to the point where I\Ndon't need the sheet music anymore...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.72,0:04:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I'll practically be sight-reading\Nwhen I coordinate the piece with her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.22,0:04:36.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And on top of that, such a...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.72,0:04:39.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Such an insanely\Nout-of-control violinist!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.16,0:04:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All set!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.24,0:04:44.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What tempo should we use?\NTake-no-prisoners, maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.11,0:04:46.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is crazy, it's reckless!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:49.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No way can I turn in a\Ndecent performance like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.98,0:04:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do I look good in this dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:53.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's brand-new.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.03,0:04:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I just man up and back out\Nof this, it won't sting as much.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.66,0:04:58.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're only gonna humiliate ourselves,\N going out like this.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.87,0:05:00.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ignoring me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.84,0:05:10.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whaaaat?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.26,0:05:12.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So tell me, did\Nthat calm you down?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:15.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea,\Nall of a sudden?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.14,0:05:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.47,0:05:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look up, and look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.72,0:05:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're always looking down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're imprisoned\Ninside that cage of music scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, I know you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.19,0:05:32.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were listening to it\Nall during lunch break, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:36.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The sheet music was always\Nsomewhere in view, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.99,0:05:39.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know you and I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mozart's telling us from up in the sky...\N"Go on a journey," he's saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.63,0:05:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"A man away from home\Nneed feel no shame."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.54,0:05:52.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go out there and\Nshame ourselves like crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.38,0:05:53.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Together...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.09,0:05:58.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. 14, Ms. Kaori Miyazono,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.68,0:06:00.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,please get ready to go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.56,0:06:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.24,0:06:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening, Kousei?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.91,0:06:20.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just what the score calls for...\NIt's all there in the sheet music.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.16,0:06:25.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Naïve... Bizarre...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.62,0:06:29.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's like I'm on a rollercoaster.\NI'm being jerked around and around.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.63,0:06:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's like this girl herself is the\Njourney with no clear destination.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.51,0:06:39.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're freedom itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.26,0:06:42.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm not.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.39,0:06:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Music is freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:07:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This silence belongs to us.\NEvery single person here...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:04.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is waiting for us to\Nstart producing sounds.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.00,0:07:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, let's go on a journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:14.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saint-Saëns is waiting for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.22,0:07:23.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Here they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Kaori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.06,0:07:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, the accompanist is a kid, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.18,0:07:28.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.94,0:07:30.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, could that be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.32,0:07:38.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been waiting for you,\NKaori Miyazono... Hmm?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.99,0:07:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's got a different\Naccompanist. A kid, at that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.33,0:07:46.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't set my chair just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up, you slowpoke.\NAdjust it with both hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.62,0:07:51.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He somehow looks familiar...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:54.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Arima. The pianist.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:55.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Arima-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that kid's\NKousei Arima, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.13,0:08:04.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right. He's grown up since then, but\Nthat's the face of the pianist, Arima...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:06.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei Arima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.35,0:08:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So they know each other?\NActually, why is he accompanying her?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.69,0:08:12.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Finally got it right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.95,0:08:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.02,0:08:19.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh. Synthetic and all-natural.\NTalk about a mismatched couple!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.78,0:08:23.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What kind of performance\Ndo you have planned?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.16,0:08:33.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Elohim, Essaim... Elohim,\NEssaim... I implore you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your face is totally frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.89,0:08:50.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A song dedicated to the\Nvirtuoso violinist, Sarasate.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.69,0:08:55.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Saint-Saëns's Introduction\Nand Rondo Capriccioso.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.70,0:09:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, that was a good start.\NI can hear the notes, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:17.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm glad we're doing this song.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.14,0:09:28.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are some parts\Nwhere I could go off-key,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:32.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but if I listen closely to the violin,\Nand keep an eye on the sheet music...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:36.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Technically, it's not a difficult song.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:40.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah... Kousei's playing\Nthe piano again...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.19,0:09:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaori Miyazono... In a complete\Ndeparture from her previous performance,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.86,0:09:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}she's being docile here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Out of consideration\Nfor Arima, maybe?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And now she's showing her true colors!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.23,0:10:19.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.97,0:10:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The notes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.64,0:10:58.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're vanishing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:11.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sound of the piano...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.57,0:11:13.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't hear it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.01,0:11:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh? What's going on?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.88,0:11:31.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? The accompanist...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:33.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sound is out of sync.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:38.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The accompanist who\Nnever played a false note,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}who played with such\Nstunning precision...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:42.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...is starting to unravel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.82,0:11:51.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As if I'm at the bottom of a\N dark sea, I can't hear anything.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.74,0:11:55.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no one here.\NIt's dark.. It's dark...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.45,0:11:59.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's dark. I'm at the\Nbottom of a dark sea...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.25,0:12:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...and I'm going to be all alone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.68,0:12:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's pounding on the keys, but\Nthis isn't the accompaniment, is it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.68,0:12:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This accompanist blows.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.10,0:12:19.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Too bad, I did like the violin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.31,0:12:22.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In spite of your inexperience,\Nyou were holding your own till now.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What got into you\Nall of a sudden, Arima?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.32,0:12:28.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The piano is destroying this performance!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.78,0:12:32.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dammit, dammit, dammit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.82,0:12:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm pounding the keys so hard...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So why?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.99,0:12:38.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is it that the only thing I\Ncan't hear is my own playing?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:05.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Probably a smart move.\NA deduction's inevitable,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but if he keeps on playing,\Nit could affect the violinist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.36,0:13:14.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lousy piano playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.78,0:13:15.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess it up for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.91,0:13:18.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't have been\Nplaying from the start!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.70,0:13:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sorry... If I keep playing like this...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.16,0:13:26.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I play... I'll only\Nmake trouble for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:56.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Now even the\Nviolinist's stopped playing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Does this mean\Nthey're disqualified?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:17.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, not disqualified, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is unheard of!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:22.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's over for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.14,0:14:24.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why did she stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.14,0:14:26.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's no reason for her to\Naccommodate that awful accompanist...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.31,0:14:28.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And she was so cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.82,0:14:33.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't worry.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.19,0:14:36.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know you and I can do it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hereby appoint you as my accompanist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.79,0:14:44.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You still have to play!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.83,0:14:47.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I want you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.58,0:14:51.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to play with everything I've got.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.67,0:14:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that the people who've heard me...\N...will never forget me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.97,0:14:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm a musician, after all!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:05.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.23,0:15:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe there's only a\Ndark road up ahead.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.02,0:15:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you still have to\Nbelieve and keeping going.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Believe that the stars will light\Nyour path, even a little bit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.79,0:15:28.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.37,0:15:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's go on a journey!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.02,0:15:52.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are they allowed to start over?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's allowed as long as it's\Nwithin the time limit,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.11,0:15:57.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but nothing after\Nthey stopped will count.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.32,0:16:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This competition is over for that girl now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:03.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:06.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...what exactly is she playing for?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.95,0:16:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Kousei? Are you\Ngonna make Kaori-chan play by herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.33,0:16:12.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.96,0:16:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For you...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.09,0:16:21.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For you... I'm casting about\Nfor an excuse again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.60,0:16:26.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know you and I can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.22,0:16:29.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There was resolve in your eyes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:33.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So what was it that you saw in me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.77,0:16:36.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you have me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:39.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look up, and look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.74,0:16:43.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Look at me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.41,0:16:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Brace yourself...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.50,0:16:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now we're talking!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.08,0:16:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He started playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.54,0:16:57.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But they still sound out of sync.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.59,0:16:59.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What are you going to do, Arima?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.92,0:17:02.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Focus... Focus...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.80,0:17:04.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Focus!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.89,0:17:08.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Both the sound and the notes are\Ndisappearing like nobody's business.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.18,0:17:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All week long, the sheet music\Nwas always where I could see it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.60,0:17:16.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All during my lunch\Nbreaks, I listened to it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:19.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whatever I have inside of\Nme... Draw it out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Focus, focus... focus...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.28,0:17:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Focus!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.28,0:17:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening, Kousei?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.58,0:17:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't play so violently.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.54,0:17:34.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The piano is you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.67,0:17:37.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you touch it gently, it will smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.29,0:17:39.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you pound it with force,\Nit will become enraged.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:42.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Touch it like you're\Ncaressing a baby's head.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:44.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All right, again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.55,0:17:55.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twinkle, twinkle, little star...\NHow I wonder what you are...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:18:07.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Up above the world so high...\NLike a diamond in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.12,0:18:17.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twinkle, twinkle, little star...\NHow I wonder what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.05,0:18:27.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you can't hear the sound,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.93,0:18:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}then imagine it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.55,0:18:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Play it with your whole body!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.60,0:18:34.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Draw out what Mom left me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.79,0:18:53.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, come on, Friend A...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.33,0:18:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't you dare try\Nto steal my thunder!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.34,0:19:06.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you kidding me?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.84,0:19:10.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Kousei! Kao-chan!\NYou're amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.30,0:19:12.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:17.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, this is outrageous. They're both\Nout of control. It's like a brawl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.19,0:19:22.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the audience is\Nentranced by this brawl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.88,0:19:46.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Of course he's not used to this.\NHe's not an accompanist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:49.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's a soloist, just like her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.05,0:19:53.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She moves me.\NWith such power,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.47,0:19:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}like the pounding of my heart.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.18,0:19:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can hear your sound.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:01.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.92,0:20:24.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}April will be ending soon.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.09,0:20:32.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.26,0:20:33.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were great,\Nmiddle school duo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.76,0:20:34.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:36.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Encore!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.48,0:20:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,During a serious competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.10,0:20:45.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dry air-conditioning,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the scent of dust.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.19,0:20:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.36,0:20:54.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going on a journey.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.10,0:21:20.08,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Departure
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.05,0:22:38.95,Next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 5\NDark Skies
